Property Description: 1293-1295 South Road, St Marys is a high quality location for the next stage of your business or an investment opportunity with great exposure to South Road.

Offered with holding income until early next year, the property allows the lucky incoming purchaser plenty of time to ensure a clear plan is in place for the future of the property. The property incorporates 25 onsite car parks and has a plenty of flexibility to adjust the internal layout to suit a wide range of businesses (STCC). 

Key investment highlights include; 
• Functional showroom and associated warehousing totaling 1,675sqm*
• High quality warehouse component including mezzanine storage
• Corner land holding of some 2,290sqm
• Leased to Forpen Pty Ltd t/a Clark Rubber expiring 16th February 2021
• Current net income of $147,804 p/a
• 25 valuable carparks on site 
• Located adjacent Tonsley Innovation District

FOR SALE VIA PRIVATE TREATY SEEKING OFFERS OVER $2.1M

Approx*.

For more information please contact the listing agents.

- Gross building area of 560 sqm*
- Versatile office, reception and amenities of 90 sqm*
- Functional medium clearance warehouse/workshop of 470 sqm*
- Good truck access and loading.
- Excellent inner south location on a corner site, only metres from South Road.
- Available 1 February 2011.

* approx.

* Gross building area of 222 sqm approx.
* Well presented office and amenities of 100 sqm approx.
* Good clearance, clear span warehouse of 122 sqm approx plus a mezzanine of 48 sqm approx.
* Racking and telephone system included.
* Ample off-street parking.
* Available now.
